data.text:
LA JOYA DE ISLAND MOORINGS GEM! Gorgeous home in gated community with boat lift! Ground floor entry opens to a beautiful, open dining/living/kitchen. Also on this floor youll find a powder room, laundry room, spacious primary suite, fabulous covered patio with fireplace, and deck with hot tub. Upsta... irs is a second living area, storage, two guest bedrooms and two guest baths. A 2-car garage affords storage of all your beach gear, too! Comes with a 35' boat slip outfitted with a boat lift. La Joya de Island Moorings has a gorgeous chilled swimming pool complex and a community marina. Located in the golf cart district with easy boating access to marinas, bay & Gulf, and easy golf cart access to the beach, airport, marina, golf course, shops & dining! Sold partially furnished. High X flood zone! Don't Miss the Boat!
